body:
Welcome To My Page.

./ Introduction

Hello my name is Bruno and I'm interested in computers and programming. I like to do level design and make sounds and music.

./ What I'm working on.

I am working on a project with Quinn Painter, Daniel Muller and Kevin Burke. Quinn and Kevin are mainly working coding. Daniel is working on gun models and I am working on level design. We are making a Massive Multiplayer FPS.

./ What I want to achieve.
I want to learn how to code better. I want to also learn how to make level's look much better and I want to make better sounds and/or music.

Bruno Torres
